Value:
do                                  \
    {                                   \
        srcId = data.tra_data_format.source;                \
    if (OCTEON_IS_MODEL(OCTEON_CN68XX) && srcId <= 7)       \
    {                               \
        srcId = tra_unit + srcId * 4;               \
        if (srcId >= 16)                        \
            srcId += 16;                        \
    }                               \
    } while (0)

Internal use function.

This function's parameters and processing may change in future SDKs.

Setup the trace buffer filter command mask. The bit position of filter commands are different for each Octeon model.

Parameters:
filter Which event to log
Returns:
Bitmask of filter command based on the event.
